(65, 1, '2026-07-13 15:45:55', '2026-07-13 09:45:55', '<h2>📋 Item Overview</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Era:</strong> Napoleon III / Late 19th Century (c. 1880)</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Origin:</strong> France</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Materials:</strong> Beveled Lead Crystal & Fire-Gilded Bronze (Ormolu)</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 6.5\" W x 4.5\" D x 5.2\" H</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Condition:</strong> Excellent Antique Condition (Extremely minor age-appropriate wear to the gilding; no chips or cracks to the crystal)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>🔍 Detailed Description</h2>\r\n<p>Up for absolute auction is a breathtaking monument to 19th-century European craftsmanship: a <strong>French Ormolu and Baccarat Style Beveled Crystal Jewelry Casket</strong>. Hailing from the height of the Belle Époque, this decorative masterpiece beautifully merges architectural structure with delicate artistry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The box features thick, heavy crystal panels, each meticulously hand-beveled to catch and refract light with magnificent brilliance. The panels are housed within an ornate, fire-gilded bronze (ormolu) framework decorated with classical motifs, featuring intricate scrolling foliage, acanthus leaf feet, and a functioning locking mechanism with its original tasseled key. Pieces of this caliber were the crowning jewels of aristocratic vanity tables and remain highly coveted focal points for discerning collectors of fine decorative arts.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>📊 Condition & Provenance Report</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li><strong>Crystal Integrity:</strong> Outstanding clarity. The heavy lead crystal panels are free from clouding, deep scratches, flea bites, or structural fractures.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Ormolu Framework:</strong> The bronze casting retains its original, vibrant 24k fire-gilded luster with a rich, authentic patina nestled into the filigree details.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Mechanism:</strong> The original hinge operates smoothly with no warping, alignment issues, or wobble. The lock turns securely.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>📦 Premium Art Shipping & Handling</h2>\r\n<p>Due to the delicate nature and historical value of this antique, professional handling is guaranteed:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n  <li><strong>Museum-Grade Packing:</strong> Double-boxed with custom-molded, shock-absorbing materials to ensure absolute immobility during transit.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Insured Global Shipping:</strong> Sent via priority courier with full declared-value insurance and mandatory signature tracking.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'French Ormolu & Baccarat Crystal Jewelry Casket', 'An exquisite capsule of Belle Époque luxury, featuring hand-beveled Baccarat crystal secured in a masterfully gilded French ormolu framework.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'french-ormolu-baccarat-crystal-jewelry-casket', '', '', '2026-07-13 15:47:02', '2026-07-13 09:47:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=65', 0, 'product', '', 0),
