ction rear differential.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Exterior & Trim:</strong> Flawless Marina Blue paint polished to a mirror finish. Brand new, correct white convertible soft top and a immaculate chrome bumper package. Equipped with iconic 15-inch turbine-style bolt-on wheels wrapped in redline tires.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Interior:</strong> Fully restored cabin featuring correct blue bucket seats, factory AM/FM radio, telescoping steering wheel, and fully functional, crisp dashboard instrumentation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>📜 Provenance & Documentation</h2>\r\n<p>To preserve your investment, this Corvette is accompanied by an extensive historical file:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Original Tank Sticker (Order Copy) validated and preserved.</li>\r\n  <li>Complete photo-documentation folder detailing the step-by-step frame-off restoration process.</li>\r\n  <li>A thick binder of service receipts, component part numbers, and ownership history.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>📦 Transport & Delivery</h2>\r\n<p>We provide global logistics support to ensure this collector-grade vehicle arrives safely at your garage:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n  <li><strong>Enclosed Transport Only:</strong> Shipped exclusively via a climate-controlled, hard-sided enclosed vehicle transporter.</li>\r\n  <li><strong>Pre-Delivery Inspection:</strong> Handed over after a thorough mechanical inspection, fluid check, and professional detail.</li>\r\n</ol>', '1967 Chevrolet Corvette Sting Ray Convertible (427/435 HP Tri-Power) (Copy)', 'An iconic American masterpiece featuring a matching-numbers 427 L71 V8 engine, iconic stinger hood, and a breathtaking, award-winning frame-off restoration.', 'trash', 'open', 'closed', '', '__trashed', '', '', '2026-07-13 16:18:36', '2026-07-13 10:18:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=75', 0, 'product', '', 0);
